tika.dc.description:
The steamy, explosive conclusion to Nelle L’Amour’s suspenseful new erotic romance.

SARAH: I have a secret that threatens to destroy him.

ARI: My past has come back and threatens to destroy her.

When the past and the present collide, the passionate journey of two star-crossed lovers is thrown off course. Life or death awaits them. Derailed, will Ari and Sarah get back on track or will they crash and burn before they get to their final destination?

**
